column5: Only a couple of months ago, yet seems like a lifetime.
A good walleye shore lunch in Ontario can't be beat.
That would pair nicely with a frosty cold beverage brewed in Canada. It's hard to beat a shore lunch!

I got home just 2 weeks ago and already trying to figure out if i can sneak back up in mid to late sept. even if it is a quick 4 days. surely some camps are not full then and looking to make a deal for a little more money????????
Dang, that looks GOOD! Mouth watering...that will stack up against any restaurant any day!
